We ruled that school.

01:45.750 --> 01:47.707
This year,
nobody likes us.

01:47.790 --> 01:49.000
That is true.

01:49.082 --> 01:51.000
Speak for yourself.
I'll be fine.

01:51.082 --> 01:52.917
I got a mustache coming in.

01:53.500 --> 01:54.790
- I don't see it.
- Nope.

01:56.750 --> 01:57.956
- Mmm-mmm.
- Nope.

01:58.040 --> 02:00.540
- Uh-uh.
- No one's got it worse than me.

02:01.417 --> 02:02.665
See that girl over there?

02:02.832 --> 02:05.292
She's gonna torture me
every chance she gets.

02:05.375 --> 02:07.209
Wait a sec.
Isn't that your sister?

02:07.500 --> 02:08.539
Yeah.

02:09.875 --> 02:11.707
At least you guys
have your own rooms.

02:11.790 --> 02:13.250
My grandfather stole mine.

02:13.334 --> 02:15.459
Wait. Your grandpa
moved in with you guys?

02:15.540 --> 02:16.625
When did that happen?

02:16.790 --> 02:18.790
Ever since he robbed
that grocery store.

02:32.540 --> 02:33.582
Can I help you, sir?

02:34.209 --> 02:36.792
- You can help me find Maria.
- Oh, Maria's gone.

02:36.875 --> 02:38.540
We're completely
self-checkout now.

02:38.625 --> 02:40.209
Much faster.
Much more efficient.

02:40.292 --> 02:41.417
I think you'll like it.

02:41.707 --> 02:42.957
So, are the prices
gonna be lower

02:43.042 --> 02:44.250
because I'm doing
all the work now?

02:44.334 --> 02:46.250
We have everyday
low prices here, sir.

02:46.625 --> 02:47.875
- Every day.
- Every day?

02:47.957 --> 02:49.707
- Every day.
- Get out of my way. Get out of my way.

02:49.957 --> 02:51.167
Oh, no problem.

02:51.957 --> 02:53.000
Whoa!

02:53.082 --> 02:54.875
<i>Please scan your item.</i>

02:54.957 --> 02:56.457
I'm talking to a robot.

02:56.540 --> 02:58.000
<i>Please scan your item.</i>

02:58.082 --> 02:59.082
I just did.

03:01.292 --> 03:02.457
See if this thing...

